                The App was created using C#, ASP.NET Core, and implementing the MVC design pattern.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-12">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-light">
                <a class="nav-link text-light" asp-area="" asp-controller="Contacts" asp-action="Index">APP</a>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
